description:
Hello every pony  
 
sorry resently i don't take any request, for i take some music compossing cases, and it's a presure... so once again i apology for those who wish for request    
 
Tomorrow i will send my Notebook back to ASUS to check some problem, it could be take some days, i decides to giving a last artwork before i can say goodbye to my working parther ,my computer. and who knows.. my mom maybe right, she always tell me to take a few days for relax... maybe this is a chance.   
Ok, enough chit chat, allow me to present Princess Ember as Ballet girl.    
 
Well, She is actually not the student in Canterlot Royal Ballet Academy, but just been invited by Princess Celestia to visit this school and have some "Fun experience",so basically , it's a diplomacy (!?)sort of...     
This ballet dress was the desgin from Balle Arcadeia, the famous pegasus desginer from Canterlot, and the leader of the brand Coeily, This dress was used to desgined for Fleur de lis, the beautiest ballerina in school's history, and it was pink 
 
and the dress for princess Ember's is violet, for the desginer thought this color is suitable for the princess.   
 
well... ok... My lady, calm down. no one will see you...(whisper to myself with Cave Johnson's voice) Nope, couldn't keep the stright face     
 
and of course you can keep the dress , don't act like you know nothing my lady, we all can hear you, right? my audience? and these toys are academy's property, sorry you can't take it, but you can play it anytime at school, or you can buy some in Canterlot's toysmarket on 3rd street.     
 
and i hope you enjoy it too, goodbye ,my PC, well... for a while, make sure you get fixed well or I'll kill you myself. not you, my fans,you're doing fine.    
 
Sean.M
